**Description:**  
Creates a new audience in the connected Google Ads account.
**Preconditions:**  
- Authenticated Google Ads account  
- Unique audience name
**Postconditions:**  
- Audience created and listed in Google Ads UI  
- Row inserted into `googleCustomAudiences` DB table
